flowchart LR
  GB[GameBootstrapper]:::neutral
  P[Planetoid]:::planet
  GBODY[GravityBody]:::orbiter
  SL[SlingshotLauncher]:::orbiter
  DF[DebrisField]:::debris
  DFC[DebrisFieldConfig]:::neutral
  SDV[StuckDebrisVisual]:::debris

  GB -.->|enables EnhancedTouchSupport<br/>before any Awake| SL

  SL -->|reads Position,<br/>SurfaceRadius,<br/>GetGravityAcceleration| P
  SL -->|Instantiate +<br/>Launch / SetPosition| GBODY
  SL -->|reads G off prefab| GBODY

  GBODY -->|reads GetGravityAcceleration,<br/>GetDragAtPoint| P
  GBODY -->|RegisterOrbiter /<br/>UnregisterOrbiter| DF

  DF -->|reads GetGravityAcceleration,<br/>AtmosphereRadius,<br/>SurfaceRadius| P
  DF -->|reads ColliderRadius, Pos;<br/>calls Absorb| GBODY
  DF -.->|reads tunables| DFC
  DF -->|Instantiate| SDV

